msgstr "今日已探索"

msgid "Sail out and gather ingredients from the islands."
msgstr "出海，从岛屿上采集食材。"

msgid "Something's stirring past the reef — go and take a look."
msgstr "礁石那头有动静 —— 去看看吧。"

msgid "Word of your cooking is spreading. Keep the orders coming."
