msgstr "%s ×%d   (+%d%s)"

msgid "You already know how to make %s!\nHere are %d coins instead."
msgstr "你已经知道如何制作 %s 了！\n这里给你 %d 金币代替。"

msgid "×%d"
msgstr "×%d"

msgid "Bring me 2 roasted dishes, Tier 2 or better — the festival crowd is hungry!"
msgstr "给我带2份烤制菜肴，星级要在2星或以上 —— 节日人群正饿着呢！"

msgid "Chickpeas + Lemon + Olive Oil → [Mixing Bowl]"
msgstr "鹰嘴豆 + 柠檬 + 橄榄油 → [搅拌碗]"

msgid "Eggplant → [Oven]"
msgstr "茄子 → [烤箱]"

msgid "No dishes this time? No worries — come back when your kitchen's been busy!"
msgstr "这次没带菜来？别担心 —— 厨房忙完了再来吧！"

msgid "Potato → [Oven]"
msgstr "土豆 → [烤箱]"

msgid "The judges are delighted!"
msgstr "评委们很高兴！"

msgid "Tomato → [Oven]"
msgstr "番茄 → [烤箱]"

msgid "Veg → [Prep] ·2 → [Mixing Bowl] +Olive Oil → [Oven]"
msgstr "蔬菜 → [备料] ·2 → [搅拌碗] +橄榄油 → [烤箱]"

msgid "Veg → [Prep] → [Mixing Bowl] +Olive Oil"
msgstr "蔬菜 → [备料] → [搅拌碗] +橄榄油"

msgid "Welcome to the Trade Fair! Present your finest dishes for the judges."
msgstr "欢迎来到贸易集市！向评委们展示你最拿手的菜肴吧。"

msgid "Your recipe codex. Every dish you cook for the first time is recorded here, along with the ingredients and stations it takes to make it."
msgstr "你的菜谱宝典。每一道你第一次制作的菜肴都会被记录在这里，以及制作它所需的食材和料理台。"

msgid "Assign a tamed spirit to a pot and it'll grow crops while you sleep, collected each morning. Careful: removing a spirit from a pot sends it away for good."
msgstr "将驯服的精灵放入锅中，它就会在你睡觉时种植作物，并在每天早上收集。注意：从锅中移除精灵会使其永久消失。"

msgid "At the Trade Fair, submit your dishes to the judges — better dishes earn more coins, and you'll climb the Explorer League ranks. No pressure: bring what you've got."
msgstr "在贸易集市上，向评委提交你的菜肴 —— 更好的菜肴可以赚取更多金币，你也可以提升探险家联盟的等级。别有压力，带上你现有的东西就行。"

msgid "Catch the falling fruit! Dodge durians, bombs, and beehives — getting hit costs you time."
msgstr "接住掉落的水果！躲避榴莲、炸弹和蜂窝 —— 被击中会扣除你的时间。"

msgid "Click ingredients to fill the slots, then Confirm. The Prep table chops, the Mixing Bowl combines, and the Oven bakes — chain them to build a dish. Add spices to a finished dish for extra stars!"
msgstr "点击食材填入插槽，然后点击确认。备料区切碎，搅拌碗混合，烤箱烘烤 —— 链式操作以制作菜肴。在做好的菜中加入香料以获得额外的星级！"

msgid "Commissions ask for dishes of a certain kind and quality. There's no deadline — deliver whenever you're ready (a little sooner earns a bonus). Bring the dishes to the NPC who asked."
msgstr "委托需要特定种类和质量的菜肴。没有截止日期 —— 随时准备好就去交付（稍微提早可以获得奖励）。把菜肴带给提出要求的 NPC 即可。"

msgid "Feed the spirit to fill its Well-Fed meter before its turns run out. Fill it to befriend it — or it'll slip away, leaving a little gift behind."
msgstr "在回合结束前喂食精灵，填满其饱食度。填满以和它成为朋友 —— 否则它会悄悄溜走，留下一小份礼物。"

msgid "Heading back early? Any nodes you haven't visited on this island are lost — but your remaining Time can still be spent elsewhere."
msgstr "要提早回去吗？本岛上你未访问的任何节点都将丢失 —— 但你剩余的时间仍可以在其他地方使用。"

msgid "Hover an island to preview its nodes. Click to sail there. Each node you explore spends 1 Time from today's budget."
msgstr "悬停在一座岛屿上以预览其节点。点击以航行到那里。你探索的每个节点都会消耗今天预算中的 1 点时间。"

msgid "This spirit has refined taste — it only accepts a cooked dish of the right kind and quality (its craving is shown above). Cook one and feed it here to win it over."
msgstr "这只精灵的口味很挑剔 —— 它只接受特定种类和质量的烹饪菜肴（它的渴望显示在上方）。做一份并在此处喂食以赢得它的好感。"
